Parameters

none

Returns

n/a

See Also

MQA.MapCornerPlacement

Note

MQA.MapCorner is not instantiated directly.  The following static values should be used:

  • MQA.CORNER_TOPLEFT
  • MQA.CORNER_TOPRIGHT
  • MQA.CORNER_BOTTOMLEFT
  • MQA.CORNER_BOTTOMRIGHT
